company_name: SARL AGRICOLE DE FAMILLE FERME DE LA MOUCHERE
information: The company SARL AGRICOLE DE FAMILLE FERME DE LA MOUCHERE, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1986, which operates in the Common wheat industry. It also operates in the cereals, soya, and maize industries. It is based in Saint-Cyr La Rosière, France.
